dct_title_s: A map of Princeton: Borough, Campus, Township (Front Side 1952)
dct_description_sm: Main buildings are shown pictorially. Street guide and points of interest are located. Title from panel. Campus map oriented with north to the lower left. Includes indexes Princeton University Press. Alternate title from panel:" A map of Princeton, Borough, Campus, Township". Main buildings are shown pictorially. Ancillary map on recto: "Forrestal Research Center main buildings"; text. Verso: "Borough of Princeton and nearby residential areas", (1:16,000); " Princeton Township showing connecting routes and principal through streets" (1:30,000). Street guide and points of interest are located.
